properties.full_description: Spend more time with parents, kids and your beloved one around Royal Gourmet® classic 6-burner stainless steel LP gas grill in your backyard! The grill features a total of 71,000 BTUs cooking power over 5 stainless steel tube burners (10,000 BTUs each), a U-shape searing burner (12,000 BTUs), and a lidded side burner (9,000 BTUs). The searing burner is powerful enough to lock in juices on any fine cut of meat, and the lidded side burner (9,000 BTU) is a perfect match for side dishes. Porcelain-enameled cooking grates distributes heat evenly across the generous cooking area of 598 sq. Inches area. The swing-away warming rack offers a secondary cooking area of 199 sq. Inches. Electronic ignition system provides quick start-up with a simple push. Efficient grease management system facilitates easy and effortless clean-up. The double-layer lid ensures excellent heat retention. LP tank and other large grill necessities can be stored in the bottom cabinet. Lockable casters allow for free movement.Ã‚?This grill is designed to satisfy all the needs and wants of avid grilling fans. Don’t hesitate, take it home and show it off at your BBQ party! Mouth-watering friends will come around, and even envious neighbors will knock at your door!

properties.full_description: Fire up your family reunion or large patio party with Royal Gourmet® mirage two split lid, 6-burner liquid propane, infrared burner gas grill with side burner. Two stainless steel lids with cast aluminum end caps keep heat during the cooking, and let you cook different kinds of food in either firebox. Porcelain cast iron cooking grates with slope design trap oil imparting a better flavor to meat. Sturdy stainless-steel side tables with plastic end cap, also provide the hooks for tools. An enclosed stainless-steel cabinet with stainless-steel doors provides storage space for both LP tank and other grill necessities. Moving the behemoth is just a piece of cake, with four flexible casters that feature brake system for quick stop.

properties.full_description: The popular and economical Weber Spirit family of gas grills adds a more fully featured E-330 model to the lineup in 2016. The new Spirit E-330 BBQ grill includes a handy 10,000 BTU side burner for cooking accompaniments and a 7,500 sear station burner that boots heat to quickly sear foods, then turns off for regular grilling. Other features include long-lasting porcelain-enameled cooking grates and porcelain-enameled Flavorizer bars. Positioned above the burner tubes and below the grates, these V-shaped bars shield burner tubes from port-clogging debris. They also serve to catch and vaporize food drippings, creating the smoke that flavors food. The Spirit E-330 LP gas grill carries a 10-year warranty on the porcelain-enameled lid and burner tubes and a 5-year warranty on grates and Flavorizer bars. Not available in natural gas.
